sequenceDiagram
    title Sequence Diagram - Admin Bulk Assign Reports

    participant Admin as "Administrator (User)"
    participant Frontend
    participant AdminController
    participant AdminService
    participant ReportRepository
    participant SchedulerService
    participant NotificationService

    Admin->>Frontend: 1) Select multiple reports and choose "Bulk assign" to officer X
    Frontend->>AdminController: 2) POST /api/admin/reports/bulk-assign { reportIds[], officerId }
    AdminController->>AdminService: 3) bulkAssign(reportIds, officerId, adminId)

    AdminService->>ReportRepository: 4) findByIds(reportIds)
    ReportRepository-->>AdminService: 5) List<Report>
    AdminService->>ReportRepository: 6) updateMany(assign officerId, reportIds)
    ReportRepository-->>AdminService: 7) updatedCount

    alt if assignment triggers scheduled follow-ups or tasks
        AdminService->>SchedulerService: 8) scheduleFollowUpJobs(reportIds, officerId)
        SchedulerService-->>AdminService: 9) scheduled
    end

    AdminService->>NotificationService: 10) notifyAssignedOfficer(officerId, reportIds) [async]
    NotificationService-->>AdminService: 11) queued
    AdminService-->>AdminController: 12) 200 OK (assignedCount)
    AdminController-->>Frontend: 13) 200 OK
    Frontend-->>Admin: 14) Show confirmation "N reports assigned to Officer X"